Radio personality and businessman Tbo Touch is living proof that hard work pays off. This is as his first movie Blessers has attracted more than 46k people, who bought tickets to see this star-studded movie. To celebrate this feat, Touch thanked one of his friends Julius Malema, who used his influence to get people to buy tickets to see the movie. The movie was released on October 25 at cinemas countrywide - and it stars some of Mzansi's most prolific stars such as Connie Chiume, Kenneth Nkosi to mention a few. 